This is a repository which contains json-schema documents which map to all the constructs in 
http://activitystrea.ms/head/json-activity.html

The syntax of the schema is defined at
http://json-schema.org/

The schemas are compatible with version draft-03

To test you can use the following library:
https://github.com/garycourt/JSV 

More libraries available in http://json-schema.org/

